                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8370" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1290</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2551 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">碧桂园：会是第二个恒大吗？</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Country Garden: Will it be the second China Evergrande Group?</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">孙红梅，黄新宇，薛秋月，武晓楠</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">上海师范大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">碧桂园控股有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">建筑、建材业与房地产业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">15 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">债务危机；财务杠杆；财务风险管理；房地产新政；房地产经济</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The debt crisis; Financial leverage;Financial risk management；New Policy for real estate; Real estate economy</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023年8月10日晚，碧桂园发布了一则内部消息公告，预计截至2023年6月30日的半年度净亏损将在450亿元至550亿元人民币之间，引起市场震动。曾作为《财富》世界500强的房地产龙头企业，却在近期接连出现海外债未如期付息和半年报大幅亏损预警，这不仅引发了碧桂园股价和债券价格的大幅波动，也使得业界各相关人士担心碧桂园是否会成为第二个恒大？本案例以碧桂园债务爆雷事件为背景，结合债务危机、财务杠杆、财务风险管理等相关知识，分析碧桂园与恒大的相同与不同之处，从而突出碧桂园在房地产新政下开展自救之路是否可以扭转困境？由此引发学员进一步思考房地产债务危机产生的原因和化解的路径与方式，分析房地产新政对房地产企业今后的发展可能产生的影响。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">On the evening of August 10, 2023, Country Garden issued an internal news announcement that it expected the net loss for the half year ending June 30, 2023 to be between 45 billion and 55 billion yuan, causing market shock. Once a leading real estate enterprise in the &quot;Fortune&quot; World 500, but in the recent series of foreign debt failed to pay interest on time and the semi-annual report of a large loss warning, which not only triggered a large fluctuation in Country Garden&#39;s stock price and bond prices, but also made the industry concerned about whether Country Garden will become the second Evergrande? This case takes Country Garden debt mine explosion event as the background, combined with the debt crisis, financial leverage, financial risk management and other related knowledge, analyzes the similarities and differences between Country Garden and Evergrande so as to highlight whether Country Garden can reverse the predicament under the new real estate deal to carry out self-rescue road? This leads to students further thinking about the causes of the real estate debt crisis and the path and way to resolve it, and analyzes the possible impact of the new real estate deal on the future development of real estate enterprises.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《会计学》、《财务管理》、《公司理财》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务杠杆；财务风险管理；债务危机与应对；房地产经济</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-06</td>
                            </tr>
